@node History "In the beginning...."

0.0ß  A fixed-size window with 2 1-pixel-wide bars

0.1ß  Made a kind of pie-diagram indicator of it...

0.2ß  Still a fixed-size window... The bars came in...

0.3ß  The fragmented memory indication

@{b}0.4ß@{ub}  A resizeable window!! Font sensitive!! Better GFX card support!!
      @{b}First limited release!!!@{ub}
@endnode
